'''沙恩·柏德烈·李維斯頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Shaun Patrick Livingston'''}}，{{bd|1985年|9月11日|||L}}），出生於[[伊利諾伊州|伊利諾伊州]]，是一名[[美國|美國]]已退役[[NBA|NBA]]職業[[籃球|籃球]]運動員，為一名[[雙能衛|雙能衛]]。他在完成高中學業後，便在2004年NBA選秀中以第一輪第四順位獲[[洛杉磯快艇|洛杉磯快艇]]選中，得以進入NBA。

2007年，李維斯頓遭受嚴重膝傷，左膝幾乎完全受損，花了一年半才康復，重回球壇。其後，李維斯頓曾先後加入[[邁阿密熱火|邁阿密熱火]]、[[奧克拉荷馬城雷霆|奧克拉荷馬城雷霆]]、[[華盛頓巫師|華盛頓巫師]]、[[夏洛特黃蜂|夏洛特山貓]]、[[密爾沃基公鹿|密爾沃基公鹿]]、[[克里夫蘭騎士|克里夫蘭騎士]]、[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]等多支NBA球隊。

2014年，他跟[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]簽約，後於[[2014-15_NBA賽季|2014-15賽季]],[[2016-17_NBA賽季|2016-17賽季]]与[[2017-18_NBA賽季|2017-18賽季]]三次獲得[[NBA總冠軍列表|NBA總冠軍]]。

== 職業生涯 ==
2004年，李維斯頓曾獲得[[杜克大學|杜克大學]]的籃球獎學金，但是宣佈放棄並直接進入NBA，在[[2004年NBA選秀|2004年NBA選秀]]中於第一輪第四順位被[[洛杉磯快艇|洛杉磯快艇]]選中，其选秀模板为[[安芬尼·哈达威|安芬尼·哈达威]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Rodger Sherman |url=http://www.sbnation.com/2015/5/20/8630123/shaun-livingston-golden-state-warriors-houston-rockets-western-conference-finals |language=en |title=Shaun Livingston's long, broken road to unlikely NBA champion |publisher=SB Nation |date=2015-06-17 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206203010/http://www.sbnation.com/2015/5/20/8630123/shaun-livingston-golden-state-warriors-houston-rockets-western-conference-finals |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當時他曾被喻為「6尺7寸的[[魔術手莊遜|魔術手莊遜]]」<ref>{{cite web |author=Bill Dwyre |url=http://www.latimes.com/sports/nba/la-sp-shaun-livingston-dwyre-20150523-column.html |language=en |title=Ex-Clipper Shaun Livingston has rebuilt knee and career with Warriors |publisher=Los Angeles Times |date=2015-05-22 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206185709/http://www.latimes.com/sports/nba/la-sp-shaun-livingston-dwyre-20150523-column.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在2007年2月26日出戰[[夏洛特山貓|夏洛特山貓]]時，一次毀滅性的膝傷幾乎終結-{}-他的運動生涯。鏡頭上只見他上籃後，在落地時扭傷左膝，接着就倒地哀嚎。他左膝幾乎每個部份都受到損害：[[前十字韌帶|前十字韌帶]]（ACL）和[[後十字韌帶|後十字韌帶]]（PCL）斷裂，[[半月軟骨|半月軟骨]]受傷，[[內側韌帶|內側韌帶]]（MCL）嚴重扭傷，[[膝蓋骨|膝蓋骨]]和[[脛腓關節|脛腓關節]]移位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2782056 |language=en |title=Livingston out for season with major knee injury |publisher=ESPN |date=2007-02-26 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206180112/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=2782056 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當時診斷的醫生曾表示可能需要截肢，但經檢驗後確認不須截肢，但在多個月的療程後始能夠行走<ref>{{cite web |author=Jonathan Abrams |url=http://grantland.com/features/on-career-shaun-livingston-survived-one-worst-injuries-nba-history/ |language=en |title=Like Magic |publisher=Grantland |date=2013-02-11 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122000348/http://grantland.com/features/on-career-shaun-livingston-survived-one-worst-injuries-nba-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該段受傷的影片被[[YouTube|YouTube]]列為限制級影片，李維斯頓本人亦未曾重看自己受傷的影片<ref>{{cite web |author=DeAntae Prince |url=http://www.sportingnews.com/nba-news/4630144-shaun-livingston-knee-injury-rehab-acl-pcl-meniscus-clippers-warriors-nets |language=en |title=Shaun Livingston never watched replay of his gruesome knee injury |publisher=ESPN |date=2014-12-17 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206175231/http://www.sportingnews.com/nba-news/4630144-shaun-livingston-knee-injury-rehab-acl-pcl-meniscus-clippers-warriors-nets |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李維斯頓被認為NBA生涯就此結束，但傷癒後亟欲尋求東山再起。

2008年6月，在近18個月的復康療程後，醫生允許李維斯頓恢復籃球活動<ref>{{cite web |url=http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/190366/Livingston-Resumes-Basketball-Related-Activities |language=en |title=Livingston Resumes Basketball-Related Activities |publisher=RealGM |date=2008-06-16 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309064652/http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/190366/Livingston-Resumes-Basketball-Related-Activities |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過，快艇隊於同年7月宣佈放棄李維斯頓<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=3481262 |language=en |title=Clippers renounce rights to Livingston, four other players |publisher=ESPN |date=2008-07-10 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206185410/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=3481262 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年10月3日，[[邁阿密熱火|邁阿密熱火]]跟李維斯頓簽下一紙兩年合約，為李維斯頓復出籃壇踏出第一步<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/heat/news/heat_sign_shaun_livingston.html |language=en |title=HEAT Sign Shaun Livingston |publisher=NBA |date=2008-10-03 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2015-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119223423/http://www.nba.com/heat/news/heat_sign_shaun_livingston.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2014-05-12/sports/fl-brooklyn-nets-news-0513-20140512_1_brooklyn-nets-miami-heat-knee-injury |language=en |title=Nets guard Shaun Livingston thankful for Heat providing second chance |publisher=SunSentinel |date=2014-05-12 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2017-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113153920/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2014-05-12/sports/fl-brooklyn-nets-news-0513-20140512_1_brooklyn-nets-miami-heat-knee-injury |dead-url=no }}</ref>。李維斯頓全季只為熱火出賽四場，平均上場10.3分鐘，場均僅獲2.3分<ref name="espn20090107">{{cite web |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=3817147 |language=en |title=Heat trade Livingston to Grizzlies |publisher=ESPN |date=2009-01-07 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109120330/http://sports.espn.go.com/nba/news/story?id=3817147 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。熱火為避免豪華稅，因此將他交易去[[孟菲斯灰熊|孟菲斯灰熊]]<ref name="espn20090107"/>，但又隨即被解僱<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.insidehoops.com/blog/?p=2968 |language=en |title=Grizzlies waive Shaun Livingston |publisher=Inside Hoops |date=2009-01-07 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150906114354/http://www.insidehoops.com/blog/?p=2968 |archive-date=2015-09-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

同年3月，李維斯頓轉投[[奧克拉荷馬城雷霆|奧克拉荷馬城雷霆]]。2009年12月，雷霆透過交易，從[[猶他爵士|猶他爵士]]獲得後衛[[艾歷克·梅諾|艾歷克·梅諾]]（Eric Maynor），釋出李維斯頓<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/thunder/news/thunder_aquires_maynor_2009_12_22.html |language=en |title=Thunder Acquires Maynor From Utah Jazz |publisher=NBA |date=2009-12-22 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2015-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151214053045/http://www.nba.com/thunder/news/thunder_aquires_maynor_2009_12_22.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年2月26日，他跟[[華盛頓巫師|華盛頓巫師]]簽下10天短約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/livingston_100226.html |language=en |title=Wizards Sign Guard Shaun Livingston |publisher=NBA |date=2010-02-26 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109120330/http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/livingston_100226.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後巫師跟他簽下餘下球季的合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/livingston_100319.html |language=en |title=Wizards Sign Livingston For Remainder of the Season |publisher=NBA |date=2010-03-19 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2014-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715001542/http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/livingston_100319.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2010-11年NBA賽季|2010-11年球季]]，他效力於[[夏洛特山貓|夏洛特山貓]]。

2011年6月23日，在公鹿、[[薩克拉門托帝王|帝王]]、山貓三方交易中，李維斯頓被交易至[[密爾沃基公鹿|密爾沃基公鹿]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/2011-06-23-bobcats-bucks-kings-trade_n.htm |language=en |title=Bobcats, Bucks, Kings work 3-way deal ahead of draft |publisher=USA Today |date=2011-06-23 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124211548/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/sports/basketball/nba/2011-06-23-bobcats-bucks-kings-trade_n.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年6月26日，他在翌年跟隊友[[喬恩·洛伊爾|喬恩·洛伊爾]]和[[瓊·布羅克曼|瓊·布羅克曼]]一起被交易至[[侯斯頓火箭|侯斯頓火箭]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/rockets-receive-12th-overall-pick-trade-bucks |language=en |title=Rockets Receive 12th Overall Pick Via Trade With Bucks |publisher=NBA |date=2012-06-26 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2015-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128204611/http://www.nba.com/rockets/news/rockets-receive-12th-overall-pick-trade-bucks |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在開季前就被釋出<ref>{{cite web |author=Tom Martin |url=http://www.thedreamshake.com/2012/10/29/3573082/rockets-trim-roster-to-15-waive-livingston |language=en |title=Rockets trim roster to 15, waive Livingston |publisher=SB Nation |date=2012-10-29 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206185649/http://www.thedreamshake.com/2012/10/29/3573082/rockets-trim-roster-to-15-waive-livingston |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年11月15日，李維斯頓再一次跟華盛頓巫師簽下合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/wizards-sign-shaun-livingston |language=en |title=Wizards Sign Shaun Livingston |publisher=NBA |date=2012-11-15 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413163637/http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/wizards-sign-shaun-livingston |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在為巫師出場17場（先發4場）後於12月23日被釋出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/wizards-waive-livingston-and-barron |language=en |title=Wizards Waive Livingston And Barron |publisher=NBA |date=2012-12-23 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413164242/http://www.nba.com/wizards/news/wizards-waive-livingston-and-barron |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩日後，同年12月25日，[[克里夫蘭騎士|克里夫蘭騎士]]在釋出[[唐納德·斯隆|唐納德·斯隆]]（Donald Sloan）後，找了李維斯頓加入球隊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/2012/news/12/25/cavaliers-shaun-livingstone-claimed.ap/index.html |language=en |title=Cavaliers claim Livingston |publisher=NBA |date=2012-12-25 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160222125713/http://www.nba.com/2012/news/12/25/cavaliers-shaun-livingstone-claimed.ap/index.html |archive-date=2016-02-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2013年7月11日，李維斯頓跟[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]簽約。李維斯頓原本只是籃網的替補後衛，但在球季中的表現良好，在翌年1月1日起開始擔任球隊的先發球員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hangtime.blogs.nba.com/2014/03/12/livingston-embodies-nets-new-identity/ |language=en |title=Livingston embodies Nets' new identity |publisher=NBA |date=2014-03-12 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206183437/http://hangtime.blogs.nba.com/2014/03/12/livingston-embodies-nets-new-identity/ |archive-date=2016-02-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2014年7月11日，李維斯頓在籃網的合約結束後，以自由球員身份跟[[金州勇士|金州勇士]]簽下合約，合約細節保密<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors-sign-livingston-20140711 |language=en |title=Warriors Sign Free Agent Shaun Livingston to Contract |publisher=NBA |date=2014-07-11 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109120330/http://www.nba.com/warriors/news/warriors-sign-livingston-20140711 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。據報導，該份為三年1600萬美元的合約<ref>{{cite web |url=http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/234077/Warriors-Reach-Three-Year-$16M-Deal-With-Shaun-Livingston |language=en |title=Warriors Reach Three-Year, $16M Deal With Shaun Livingston |publisher=RealGM |date=2014-07-01 |accessdate=2016-02-06 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215701/http://basketball.realgm.com/wiretap/234077/Warriors-Reach-Three-Year-$16M-Deal-With-Shaun-Livingston |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在他的導控之下，勇士雙槍「[[浪花兄弟_(NBA)|浪花兄弟]]」能更專注於搶分，並幫助勇士獲得睽違40年的[[NBA總冠軍列表|NBA總冠軍]]。

[[2015-16_NBA赛季|2015-16赛季]]，2016年6月2日，李維斯頓随队完成常规赛73胜的成就。李維斯頓在總冠軍賽第一戰對決[[克里夫蘭騎士|克里夫蘭騎士]]時，攻下了隊高20分，也是個人生涯季後賽新高。

[[2016-17_NBA赛季|2016-17赛季]]，李維斯頓随队第二次赢得NBA总冠军。

[[2017-18_NBA赛季|2017-18赛季]]，李維斯頓跟隨勇士隊完成二連霸。

[[2019-20_NBA赛季|2019-20赛季]]，李維斯頓宣布退休。

